If there can `&quot;` between `&quot;&quot;` then you can try this

    &quot;((?:\\&quot;|[^&quot;])*)&quot;

 - `&quot;` - Match `&quot;`
 - `((?:\\&quot;|[^&quot;]*))` - Match `\\&quot;` or anything except `&quot;` zero or more time

&lt;!-- begin snippet: js hide: false console: true babel: false --&gt;

&lt;!-- language: lang-js --&gt;

